# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Table 7: __builtins__ dict-presence — abc.ABCMeta, abc.ABC, abc.abstractmethod
#
# __builtins__ is NOT in the __dict__ of any abc construct. __builtins__ is
# a module-level name injected into module __dict__ by the Python import
